name: one man down
description:
Fine Art signed Limited edition print on Heavy PhotoRag acid free paper,
from Bristol artist Ben Barter.
Black and white and red contemporary ink drawing.
12” x 12” + 3” border. Edition of 50.
The print is not framed and is sent via special delivery, rolled in a heavyweight tube.
